<%@ page pageEncoding="UTF-8" %>
<section><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="4 4 [&quot;para&quot;,null]"><section><div class="lf-audio-card"><i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i><div><b>&#38899;&#39057;&#65306;</b>&#30707;&#38745;&#32769;&#24072;&#35775;&#35848;-&#20154;&#29983;&#19982;&#33310;&#21488;&#65288;&#19979;&#65289;<br/><span>&#21407;&#33410;&#30446;&#38899;&#39057;&#21487;&#36890;&#36807;&#21407;&#24494;&#20449;&#25991;&#31456;&#25910;&#21548;&#12290;</span></div></div></section><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;晚上好，这里是渥太华中文电台 FM97.9 兆赫，由 CHIN Radio 和渥太华华人社区服务中心联合主办，岁月如歌文艺沙龙协办。我是今晚的主持人灵兮。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">今天和我一起在直播间里的，是原创戏剧《心声》的导演、表演培训老师——石静老师。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在上一期节目中，我们聊到石静老师毕业于上海戏剧学院表演系，曾是一名职业演员。移民加拿大后，她一度离开舞台，转而从事</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">保险</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">理财工作。但她始终没有放下对艺术和表演的热爱。二十年后重返舞台，成功出演了《狗魅情缘》《日出》等剧目，可以说完成了一次凤凰涅槃式的回归。</span></span></p><section><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-02.jpg" class="lf-article-img" alt="&#30707;&#38745;&#32769;&#24072;&#35775;&#35848;&#35270;&#39057;&#23553;&#38754;" /></section><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">节目播出后，我们收到了许多听众的反馈。大家非常敬佩石静老师从专业剧场走向社区舞台，用艺术回应生命的坚持。</span></span></p></b></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-02.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7185678601165695" data-w="1201" style="width:542px;height:390px;" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><section><b style="font-weight:normal;" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p><span leaf=""><br  /></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-03.png" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="1360" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf="">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;https://youtu.be/O4Y02nCamdA?si=lkSh4hRqdPo6pfFo</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;2025 年 3 月，由您编导的原创戏剧《心声》在渥太华成功上演。演出结束后，许多观众久久不能平静，留下了非常深刻的印象。时隔一年，我们依然对这部作品记忆犹新。今晚我们就从《心声》聊起，听一听这部作品背后的故事。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;说到《心声》，我心里确实有很多故事。一年过去了，时间过得非常快。《心声》的产生，并不是一个刻意的计划，而更像是一种无意中的碰撞和缘分。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">艺术创作很多时候来自生活。你遇到的、经历过的事情，会在某个瞬间给你灵感，让你突然很想把这些体会说出来。作为演员，常常是在演别人写的故事。如果有一天你发现自己有故事想说，就不得不走向导演的位置。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">《心声》这个项目，要追溯到 2020 年。那一年，我的人生经历了一件非常重大的事情。7 月 22 日，我还和朋友一起横渡渥太华河。到了 10 月，我突然接到医生的电话，要求我立刻住院。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">之后，我接受了一系列紧急治疗。这是一种血液方面的疾病，需要进行干细胞移植。在移植之前，我经历了两次非常强烈的化疗。所有身体指标几乎降到零，然后再一点一点恢复</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，博有一种起死回生的感觉</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整个治疗过程让我产生了一种很深的感受，仿佛上帝为我打开了另一扇窗</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">让我看到一个以前完全不了解的世界。当身体健康的时候，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这个世界是被遮蔽着的，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">你看不见。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在医院里，我感受到大量的慈悲和爱。医生、护士彼此并不认识你，但他们对病人的照顾非常细致。那种被关怀、被托付的感觉，让你知道自己并不是孤单的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">其中有一位护士让我非常感动。干细胞采集那天，从早上七点半到下午四点，我必须一动不动地躺在床上。她全程陪着我，照顾我。如果没有她在身边，我无法想象那一天该如何度过。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这段经历让我深刻体会到生命的脆弱，也意识到明天和意外哪一个先来，我们永远无法预知。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这次的经历之后，我感觉我得到了第二次生命！</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-04.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6171875" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那是一种突然从“向前奔跑”进入“被迫停下”的状态。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">记得那时正在完成广播敬请剧《爱，创造奇迹》，正要进入录音的阶段。全体学员认真努力了好几个月，我不能因此而半途而废。我询问医生我是否可以继续做完广播剧的录制工作，医生说，可以，继续做完，不碍事。最后广播剧《爱，创造奇迹》得以在2020年11月的Remembrance day 播出。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">非常感恩这次经历，它让我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">真正含义上的感受到了爱与</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">慈悲。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">与此同时，世界正在发生战争。乌克兰战争爆发时，很多人以为不会持续太久，但至今仍未结束。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">那段时间，我在国家艺术中心看了一场乌克兰芭蕾舞团的演出。演出中有几幕描绘城市被摧毁后的生存状态，非常震撼。三位演员在废墟中挣扎，最后其中一人倒下，其他人试图把他抬起。那一刻我流泪了。舞蹈让人落泪并不常见，但那次真的击中了我。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">后来我又在布达佩斯旅行，看到当地民众以非常安静的方式反对战争。他们没有口号，只是放着音乐，展示巨幅照片。其中有一张照片，是穿着军装的新郎和新娘在拥抱告别。那一刻，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我的心被紧紧地抓住了。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">脑</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">海</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">中闪过很多画面和疑问：这位新郎是否还能活着回来？</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这些生活场景，对我产生了极大的冲击。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我逐渐意识到，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我是学习艺术的，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">是多么</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">想用艺术的形式回应这个世界。我得到了那么多爱</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">与呵护</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，我也希望能做点什么。我希望用艺术去表达对和平的渴望，去表达爱。因为当你真正谈论爱时，战争是无法发生的。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-05.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;正是在这样的背景下，我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">内心蠢蠢欲动，开始构思</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。《心声》这个名字，并不是一开始就确定的，而是在团队慢慢建立的过程中逐渐浮现出来的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">“心声”，英文可以理解为&nbsp;</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">Voices of the Heart</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，是发自内心的表达。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">逐渐进入创作后期时，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">突然</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">意识到，“心声”和“新生” 发音</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">是同样的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。新生，意味着新的生命。这一层含义，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">它</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">和我个人的经历密切相关。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">也许在冥冥之中，上帝对我的召唤。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在医院里，我经历了将近半年多的治疗过程，之后是漫长的恢复期。这段时间，彻底刷新了我对人生意义的理解。我意识到，我的人生轨迹已经发生了转变。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">过去，我是通过扮演别人的角色来呈现人生；现在，我想说出自己的话，讲自己</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">想要说</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">的故事。我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">必须充当</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">导演</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这个“角色”</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;在这样的状态下，团队显得非常重要。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">说的太对了！</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">团队非常重要。尤其是在</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我自己</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">身体条件并不理想的情况下，没有团队是不可能完成这样的作品的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我很幸运能</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在渥太华遇到一群非常可爱</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">和热心</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">的朋友。他们热爱戏剧、热爱表演，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">热爱艺术，热爱生活</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。很多人之前只是做朗诵、演诵，逐渐开始接触独白式的表演，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">其中注入了</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">更多表演元素。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">当他们意识到 “也许我可以试着扮演一个角色”的时候，那种蠢蠢欲动的感觉是很自然的。我觉得，如果有这样的热情，我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">非常愿意</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">去扶持。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">《心声》正好成为一个机会，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">一同努力把故事</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">说出来，用艺术的方式呈现。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-06.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7015625" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这个过程本身就已经非常不容易了。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;确实不容易。后来回想起来，我觉得这个项目的初心其实很简单，就是想做一点能够回应社会的事情，做一点有意义的事情。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整个排练过程并不轻松。七个</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">原创剧目</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，众多演员，全部是双语表演。对一个社区戏剧来说，这是一个很大的挑战。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;听说您一开始和家人讨论这个项目时，也有不少顾虑。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。我最先跟我先生谈这件事时，他非常惊讶。他知道</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我的情况</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，也</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">非常</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">清楚我以前做大型朗诵会、演出时付出的体力和精力</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，完成后经常会有一种累的只剩半条命</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">那现在我不能与以前相比，没有“命“可舍了。&nbsp;</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他说，你现在的身体还能承受这么大的消耗吗？</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">后来我跟他解释了我想做这部作品的原因，讲了我的经历，也讲了我看到的战争、看到的那些触动我的画面</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">、谈到了团队建立 等，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他听完之后非常支持。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">但他提出了一个很重要的建议。他说，我之前做的几乎都是中文作品，这样其实是不公平的。既然身在加拿大，为什么不能</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">努力一把做成双语，即，说英语，用中文字幕，说中文，用英语字幕。这样</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">可以</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">让更多不同背景的观众也能看懂、听懂</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这个建议对我来说既好，又有挑战性。我当时立刻回应他说，如果是双语作品，那你能不能做我们的英语顾问？所有英文部分由你来把关。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他答应了，也非常认真地支持了这个项目。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-07.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.7788873038516406" data-w="701" style="width:558px;height:992px;" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;-灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那这个项目从真正启动到落地，大概经历了多长时间？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;其实是在 2023 年 12 月的一次圣诞聚会上。当时大家只是在</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">随便</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">聊天，没有形成明确计划。我自己那时也非常犹豫</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">不决</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，因为这个项目的工作量实在太大了。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我有担忧。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">2023年12月28日，我的妹妹因脑溢血突然去世。在我痛苦万分的同时，我突然意识到，现在可以做的事情现在做，不要等。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">真正开始筹备，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">是在</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;2024 年 1 月，召集了几位朋友，成立了筹备组，召开了第一次正式会议。这个推进速度连我自己都感到意外。可以说，大家是一呼百应。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">那次会议，是我人生中开过的最长的一次会议。我们大约下午一点左右开始吃午饭，边吃边聊，一直聊到晚上，又点了面条继续讨论。具体几点结束我已经记不清了。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">会议的主要内容是我提出</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">一个大概得</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">构思，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">要</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">做什么样的作品，想表达什么样的主题。大家在这个基础上不断补充想法，提出建议。讨论过程中气氛非常热烈，越聊越有激情。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;剧目的选择也是在这个阶段完成的吗？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">基本上是的。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我对</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">有些</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">作品本身就非常熟悉，也一直很喜欢。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">比如《简·爱》，这是一部经典小说。无论在什么年龄去读，都会有不同的体会和理解。这正是经典作品的魅力，它跨越时代，不会过时。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">莎士比亚的作品也是如此。几百年过去了，依然具有现实意义。在《皆大欢喜》中有一句</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">台词</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，大意是</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">逆境</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">和厄运自有</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">妙处</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。这句话对我触动很深。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">当我亲身经历疾病与创伤之后，再回过头去理解这句话，会有完全不同的感受。很多看似不幸的经历，最终可能会带来另一种意义上的成长。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这种理解，似乎也和《心声》的主题非常贴合。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。我慢慢意识到，很多事情并不是简单的好与坏。关键在于你如何看待、如何转化。只要转变视角，很多经历都可以成为推动生命向前的力量。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">正是这些经历，让《心声》开始逐渐成形，也吸引了许多志同道合的人加入。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-08.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.89453125" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;在整个制作过程中，哪一部分对您来说压力最大？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;对我来说，压力最大的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">要属&nbsp;</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">招生。再好的构思，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">再好的筹备团队，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">如果没有演员参与，都是无法实现的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">像《心声》这样的项目，不是普通意义上的报名，而是要</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">通过试演 (Audition) , 经过挑选来决定谁演谁，或者，谁更合适演谁。随后参加</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">表演</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">培训</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">、进入角色</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">塑造</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。这对很多人来说，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">都</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">是第一次尝试。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我们经历了招生和筛选。这个过程并不轻松，也需要反复解释</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">什么是试演</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">并帮助</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">大家明白</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">试演与整个项目的关系。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">为了让更多人理解，我们还专门召开了一场新闻发布会，既是项目介绍，也是招生说明会。在会上，我们详细讲解了《心声》的创作理念，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">为什么要试演，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">以及参与表演需要面对的挑战。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我们的目标是让大家不要害怕。因为</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">每一个人都是独一无二的，都有自己的特点特性，就如</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">每一个角色</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">都是独一无二，有自己的特点特性。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">无论角色大小，所有演员都要经过这个过程，没有人可以例外。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这个筛选过程，对您来说是不是也很为难？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。艺术创作不像数学，无法用公式衡量。导演要判断的是这个人是否适合这个角色，而不是谁更努力，或者谁更优秀。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">有时候，并不是能力问题，而是气质、状态、契合度的问题。这些很难用语言解释清楚。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我们也遇到过一些演员非常认真，但最终没有被选中。那种时候，心里是很难受的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">后来我们尽量调整安排，让参与过招生的演员，都有机会上台，只是角色大小不同，挑战程度不同。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-09.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.66640625" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那您在选择演员时，最看重的是什么？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我最看重的是态度。只要你愿意认真投入，我相信是可以通过训练和排练逐渐成长的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">如果态度不认真，再有天赋也很难继续。表演是需要长期投入的事情。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那整部《心声》最终大概有多少演员参与？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我没有特别精确地去算过。不同剧目参与的演员数量差异大。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">《简·爱》用了五位演员；《蝴蝶夫人》是两</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">个</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">演员；《</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">游园惊梦</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">》四位演员；莎士比亚《罗密欧与朱丽叶》阳台</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">会片段</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，有三位演员</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">；《旗袍 – 当诗人遇见舞者 …》有三位演员；表演唱</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">《听妈妈讲过去的故事》12位演员；最后的表演唱《我和你》4位演员。这样算下来，整体参与的演员数量在三十</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">多</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">人。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">7个节目都是原创，导演工作量大，培训授课的工作量也大。因时间与精力有限，尽可能合理安排人力资源，我在《蝴蝶夫人》的剧本上加入了构思与具体处理文案，等“坐排”，即案头工作完成后，我交给了朱丽颖负责培训与排练，我安排几个节点参加。 另外，表演唱</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">《听妈妈讲过去的故事》</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">交给了杨虎老师来</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">负责</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">排练</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">演出结束后，很多演员都写下了自己的感想和心得。我后来看到这些文字，觉得非常感人，也说明大家在这个过程中都有真实的投入和体验。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;听起来，这是一个持续时间非常长的项目。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。从 2024 年 1 月开始筹备，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">坐排，走地位排练，连排，直到2025年3月21&amp;22的演出，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">几乎整整15个月。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">最初是招生简章、文件准备，各种基础工作。5 月召开了新闻发布会，正式启动招生。6 月开始陆续有人报名。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">当时也有人问我，如果没有人来怎么办。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">说实在的，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">自己</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">心里</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">也没有底</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，但我始终觉得，这件事是必须要做的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，就不必去多想，做就是了</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我们能做的，就是把自己该做的事情做到位，剩下的只能交给时间和命运。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-10.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="1280" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely2="396" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;后来事实证明，还是吸引了很多优秀的参与者。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。我觉得这也说明，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">还是有许多朋友热爱戏剧表演艺术，都有想尝试一下的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">愿望，只是缺少一个合适的平台。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;排练阶段对演员和导演来说，应该都是非常关键的。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。排练是整个创作过程中最重要的部分之一</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我们的排练从 2024 年 7 月底正式开始。最初是</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">坐在一起进行案头工作</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">阶段，主要是</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">通过对台词阅读剧本，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">理解剧本</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">的主题思想、中心事件</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">、</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">情景说明、</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">理解人物</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">性格与关系、等等</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。这个阶段并不是马上进入表演，而是先建立认知。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我记得，我特别强调找出每句台词背后的潜台词。潜台词是人物在行动过程中真实的内心表现，通过潜台词能传达出人物真实想法和感受。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">接下来</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">的排练进入走位/舞台调度，根据舞台上发生的事情、矛盾冲突、人物关系来确定演员站在哪里，如何移动以及角色与角色之间的空间关系，以及道具的使用。演员的培训工作也就在其中进行。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">接着进入可打断的连排，再过渡到不打断连排。这里</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">连排的意义在于</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">不打断的把整个片段走下来</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，演员开始体验</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">人物动作线的连贯性以及掌握全剧的节奏</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">再过度到全剧连排，同时加入了画外音的连结，确保演员与灯光，服装，道具，音效，化妆等舞台技术人员的沟通与配合，以达到舞台最佳艺术效果。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">到了这个阶段，演员开始</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">更清晰的把角色的动作线连贯下来，通过“真听，真看，真感觉（真思考）”的表演三要素更加深入角色</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。每一次连排，都是一次重新体验，而不是简单重复。戏剧表演不是程式化的，每一次呈现，都会因为当下的状态而有所不同。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那导演在这个阶段的工作重心是什么？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;导演的工作</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">除了培训，还要聚焦在主题思想的主线上，把握全剧（7个剧目）的整体艺术风格与叙事逻辑</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">因此，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">每一次连排之后，我都会和演员沟通，指出哪些地方是</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">进步</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，哪些地方</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">还需要</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">修</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整与提高</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这个过程就像登山。前期是在打基础，慢慢往上走；连排阶段，开始</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">从山脚下向上开始</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">攀登；到了正式演出，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">攀登山峰 - 抵达</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">山顶。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-11.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.5003909304143863" data-w="1279" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：.</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;在社区剧场的条件下，时间和人员安排应该也会带来不少挑战。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;确实如此。因为大家都有本职工作，不可能像专业剧团那样全天</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">和每天</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">排练。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">有时候会遇到演员临时缺席的情况，这对整体排练节奏影响很大。但这就是现实条件，必须接受。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我只能在有限的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">条件下，有限的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">时间内，尽量</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">把控</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整体节奏，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">尽可能多的推进剧目的艺术呈现</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;在演出临近的时候，售票是不是也成为一项重要的压力？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。演员付出了大量时间和精力，他们需要观众，需要被看到。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">戏剧创作最终是要和观众一起完成的。舞台和观众之间会形成一种互动，像电流一样，彼此回应。如果没有观众，演出是无法成立的。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在进入</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">全剧</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">连排阶段时，我们已经非常接近演出日期了，这时候售票压力就变得非常现实。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;当时票房情况如何？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">开始推售票务时遇上瓶颈，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">后来票还是卖出去了，而且两场演出都是满座。在渥太华，这样的情况并不常见。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我决定腾出时间加入推售票务的行列，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">当一定数量的票售出后，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">无形中就</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">形成了一种势能</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">与动量，那时，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整个团队的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">推票</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">状态明显发生了变化。大家开始真正动起来，有了目标感。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">对我来说，非常重要的一点是，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">剧场座无虚席 - 我</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">没有辜负演员</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">以及舞台工作人员</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">对我的信任。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-12.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.64921875" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;观众的反馈对您来说，意味着什么？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">观众喜欢与认可对全剧组是顶级的鼓励与鼓舞。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;非常重要。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">那</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">不是我一个人的工作，而是整个筹备团队共同完成的成果。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">大家</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">都投入了大量精力。正是这种集体努力，才让《心声》被更多人看见。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我一个人的能力与能量场是及其有限的。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;有没有哪一个观众的反馈，让您印象特别深刻？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;有。一位十七岁的男孩，看了两场演出。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他是后台负责耳麦管理的义工的孩子。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他已经看过三月21号的演出。22号他让他妈妈再搞一张票看演出。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">演出结束后，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他来到后台。我偶遇他，忍不住</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">问他为什么要看第二遍。他用英语回答我，说这部作品让他非常感动。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">他并没有说太多，只用了最朴实的语言。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">但是这些语言击中了我，让我深受感动。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;在创作层面上，有没有哪一部分是您觉得最困难的？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;对我来说，创作中挑战最大的是画外音的设计。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">画外音在整部作品中起到的是“龙骨”的作用，需要把七个节目串联在一起。如果画外音不到位，整体结构就会松散。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">这个部分对我来说压力很大，因为既要保证逻辑清晰，又要在情感上起到承接和过渡的作用。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-13.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;从最终呈现来看，这一部分完成得非常好。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">画外音的创作用了许多时间，圣诞新年期间全剧组休息，我撰写画外音。前后</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">经历了多次调整。包括</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">长短</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">、内容</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">取舍</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">和衔接方式</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">等，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">都反</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">反复</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">复</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">的推敲与</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">修改。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">定稿后，我还要赶着录制干声，提交给音效设计叠入音乐混录等，全剧连排时必须投入使用。最后从演出的结果来看，收到了成效。从观众反馈中许多有提到画外音。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">整个创作过程虽然经历了很多困难，但最终所有内容都踏踏实实地落地了。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我的心也落下了。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;您对“成功”这个词，似乎一直比较克制。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我一直不太愿意用“成功”来形容这次演出。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我觉得这更像是一个阶段性的完成，而不是终点。距离真正意义上的成功，还有很长的一段路。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">艺术创作本身就是不断追求的过程，而不是一个结果。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-14.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.55390625" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这种标准，和您对艺术的态度是一致的。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。我更愿意把这次演出看作一个重要的逗点，而不是句号。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;您刚刚提到“静美艺术空间”，能不能和我们介绍一下，这是一个怎样的空间？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我之所以用“空间”这个词，是因为我更看重一种状态，而不仅仅是一个具体场所。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">我喜欢在一个安静的空间里，让自己慢下来</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">做梦，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">看书听书学习审视反省，同时也会</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">产生各种各样的</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">创作</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">想法。很多灵感，往往来自生活中某一个非常细小的触动。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">所以我认为，艺术空间不一定发生在舞台上。生活本身，也可以成为艺术发生的空间。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;也就是说，它并不只是一个表演或培训的地方。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。一个小型聚会、一次主题活动、一次朋友之间的交流，都可以被创造为一个艺术空间。在这样的空间里，人们可以分享、交流、展示才艺，也可以只是单纯地感受生活。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那“静美”这个名字，有什么特别的来历吗？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;“静美”其实是我父母给我的名字。我们家女孩子是“静”字辈，本来我的名字是“石静美”。后来因为年轻时觉得两个字更简洁，就把“美”字去掉了。现在重新把“静美”这个名字用回来，是想纪念我的父母。这个名字对我来说，是一种祝福。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;听起来像是一个很完整的回归。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。我觉得这个名字，画了一个圆。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那“静美艺术空间”的活动，是固定举行的吗？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;不是固定的，是不定期的。很多活动都来自当下的灵感。有时候是一个主题，有时候只是想把一些人聚在一起，分享当下的状态。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这种形式，是从什么时候开始的？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;最早是在疫情期间。那时候无法线下聚集，只能在线上进行。大家会各自准备一个节目，围绕一个主题，用不同形式来表达。有朗诵、有表演，也有即兴创作。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我看了你们前不久的一次活动视频，感觉大家都很投入。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。每个人都带着自己的热情来参与。有一次我自己也做了即兴舞蹈。那是根据音乐当下的感受，自然地动起来，没有设计动作，也没有预设意义。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我注意到，您现在的状态，似乎比以前更开放。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我觉得表演本身是在不断变化的。以前可能更强调角色、技巧、体系，现在更关注当下的感受。只要是合适的表达方式，我都愿意去尝试。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那您怎么看待专业和业余之间的差别？在渥太华，很多热爱艺术的朋友，其实都是业余爱好者。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我觉得专业和业余之间，并不是一道不可跨越的界线。只要有热爱，有认真投入，就永远不晚。很多能力都是在实践中被唤醒的。人一出生，其实都是有表演天赋的。只是随着成长，生活把人带向了不同的方向，这一部分慢慢被放下了。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-15.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.0555555555555556" data-w="1080" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;那专业训练，会不会影响他们的发挥？</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;专业训练更多是一种潜移默化的影响。它不是限制，而是帮助。关键不在于你是否受过专业训练，而在于你愿意投入多少时间，付出多少认真。只要</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">不吝啬时间</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">有</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">一</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">份认真，就可以不断进步。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我也听到一些专业背景的朋友，看完《心声》后，对演员的表现评价很高。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;是的。有些朋友在来看演出之前，知道这是一个非专业团队，心理预期并不高。但看完之后，他们觉得整体呈现是成立的。这说明演员们是投入的，也是敬业的。这不是随便上台就能做到的。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;这背后，离不开您在排练中的引导。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我觉得这是双向的。</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">表演的培训绝对是</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">老师和</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">学生</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">在一起工作的过程。只有双方都打开心扉，往同一个方向努力，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:&#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">角色才会被塑造，</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">作品才有可能成立。这不是一个人的力量，而是集体的成果。</span></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我们的节目时间过得非常快，已经接近尾声了。非常感谢石静老师今天再次来到直播间，和我们分享《心声》背后的创作经历与思考。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;我也非常感谢有这样的机会，可以和大家分享我在艺术创作中的一些感受、创作的初心，以及创作的背景。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;也感谢您把这么真实的生命体验，通过艺术的方式呈现出来。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;也特别感谢灵兮，以及你们的组织，邀请我来到这里。如果以后还有机会，我们可以继续聊。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">灵兮：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;好的，希望我们下次再约。</span></span></p><hr style="border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);"  /><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">石静：</span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf=""><br  /></span></span><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arimo,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"><span leaf="">&nbsp;谢谢大家。</span></span></b></section><section><span leaf=""><a class="normal_text_link" target="_blank" style="" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3OTg4NTM5MQ==&amp;mid=2247487624&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2c1585344e2c84c7730d2031cfba5af3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="《心声》导演创作后记与感想" data-itemshowtype="0" linktype="text" data-linktype="2">《心声》导演创作后记与感想</a></span></section><section><span leaf=""><a class="normal_text_link" target="_blank" style="" href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3OTg4NTM5MQ==&amp;mid=2247487522&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=540b979158f9d6602f5e00ea79171b10&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="《心声》演职员感想集锦" data-itemshowtype="0" linktype="text" data-linktype="2">《心声》演职员感想集锦</a></span></section><section><span leaf=""><br  /></span></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 18px;background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255);">《心声》观众反馈</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">姚承文 （语音记录）</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">原中央戏剧学院的戏剧评论博士生的朋友的反馈非常中肯，所有的意见反馈都不能脱离《心声》艺术创作的有限条件（limited resources）作为导演，承诺了太多的导演以外的工作。演出还是很成功的，给渥太华的观众带来艺术上极大的享受。针对的观众，照顾到中文和英语，加大了创作的难度，这方面还是很成功的。选择的创作主题好！ 爱情是古今中外永恒的主题，围绕着“爱”选择戏剧片段，出发点特别好。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">艺术永远是遗憾的艺术，尤其是条件上有太多的限制，缺少资金，时间紧张，演员需要培训，对表演的基础是零，越是经典的东西越是有难度，要呈现导演想要达到的艺术要求，鉴于上述提到的困难，演员如果能达到你要求的50% 就非常不错了。 同样的这样一台艺术创作构思，试想，如果有一支专业的团队（灯，服，道，效，化，视觉艺术设计等），加上一组专业的演员，那结果就完全不一样了。旁白安排的挺好的，旁白在很大程度上弥补了创作条件演员表演上的缺憾，带给观众更专业的享受。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">当然，每个演出总是不是不完美的。比如牡丹亭-游园惊梦，中国舞台上的经典昆曲。受到舞美，灯光，布景等的局限，加之演员表演能力的限制，这个唯美的，非现实主义的故事，体现创作构思及意图是相当困难的。听妈妈讲那过去的故事，如何体现出新的表现形式，老歌新唱，欠缺新意，且也显长了。总之，这是一次非常好的，很有创新的尝试。看得出导演所付出的心血和努力。</span></span></p><p data-pm-slice="2 2 []"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">虹儿</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">祝贺石静老师担任总策划和导演的心声戏剧演出圆满成功！这是一场富有深意和温度的演出，通过舞台传递给观众的不只是感动与美好，更是一种呼唤——对世界和平的向往、对人类彼此关爱的期盼，以及对放弃仇恨、拥抱爱的深刻思考。演员们动情的表演背后，凝聚着无数次排练的汗水和坚持，令人敬佩与感动。石静老师在中英文双语背景中的深情述说，声线温暖而富有磁性，为整场演出增添了情感的厚度，直击心灵。谢谢这场精彩而深刻的‘心声’呈现，真的非常喜欢！[玫瑰][玫瑰][玫瑰]</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-16.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.8925925925925926" data-w="1080" style="width:578px;height:516px;" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p data-pm-slice="2 2 []"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">赵萍</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">石静，首先谢谢你邀请我参加心声演出。我很开心。我明天就飞回上海。因为我的角色没有替代人所以我特意等到演出结束后才回国。下星期就不能参加聚餐了。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">替我谢谢舞台导演朱莉映以及整个后天工作人员！这次演出成功离不开他们的倾心付出！当然最要感谢的人是你！我看到了你毕生的追求，那份执着令我感动[Rose]感谢，感谢</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">余劲松牧师</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">可能你在演出结束的时候，因为人声嘈杂，没有听到我说的话（跟你照相以前）我说两句话：一句是“我哭了.谢谢你！”第二句是：“你该放松休息了”[Heart]我感叹演出的阵容庞大, 环节众多，一定是一个消耗心力和体力的大项目，姊妹居然做成了！为你庆贺！也为你感恩！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">而且还是双语言。你的串场诵读，饱涵感情，字字珠机，把一台节目串起来，如同串联珍珠项链的那根金线。主题以心为核，以情为生长，合与分，现实与梦幻，西方与东方，绝望与希望，两性之情，母子之情， 一直带着我感受....，有花前月下之美好，有期盼爱情中的强烈饥渴，有情绝之时极度绝望，而浴火重生的简爱， 那种不离不弃， 回归心声的引领， 一切都烧了， 而那个爱之家才刚刚开始， 实在感人， 这就是我流泪的时刻，谢谢你的倾情付出，送给观众深刻的艺术感受[Laugh][Rose][Rose][Rose] 我想你最后的对大家的感恩也绝不是虚言，也是发于心声[Party][Party][Party][Party]</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">原博</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">话剧《心声》圆满落幕，有幸参与</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-17.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.103205629397967" data-w="1279" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">Bonita</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">感谢大家的支持！两场演出座无虚席，散场时人潮太密，有些朋友甚至没来得及当面拥抱道谢，这份热情我们全记在心里了[Party][Rose][Kiss] 谢谢@静美艺术空间 @人生如华北美持证专业健身教练 导演大大，《心声》杀疯了！请收下我的膝盖！ 每一幕皆见匠心独运，每一帧皆蕴情感澎湃。@Annie 郑小焰 服装设计让我们在舞台上闪闪发光[Grin] @红晖 让观众陶醉在我们的声音里感恩和慈悲真的是可以拯救人类的唯一方式，没有之一！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">楚红秋</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">祝贺《心声》演出圆满成功[Rose][Rose][Rose]大家的敬业精神让人动容！从各个角度都看到了细节的处理，无论是主题画外音的贯穿，形式的多样，内容无国界，演员台词及表演的处理，亮眼的服饰，得体的化妆发型，灯光道具切换，音响效果，甚至谢幕环节，等等，无不透露了缜密细致的准备工作必须给一个大大的赞</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">党梅贞</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">石静，衷心祝贺你的这台节目的演出圆满成功！[Rose][Rose][Rose][Rose] 非常感人。知道你们付出了多少心血，节目来之不易！ 我两个晚上都来了。所以看了两遍。 我为你感到骄傲! 你的搞一台经典片段从一个种子到最后成了果实,好好回味！希望你没有累坏。好好歇歇。我们回头再聊。为你骄傲,穿插全场的旁白是画龙点睛，穿针引线和承上启下的杰作。真的是导演从心里发出来的声音—心声</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">小军，（在水一方）</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">热烈祝贺“心声”首场演出取得巨大成功！构思非常新颖。编剧，导演，配乐，表演，灯光和字幕都大大超出我的期望。您的朗诵是第一流的[ThumbsUp] 感人至深。‘’心声‘’是您的嘔心瀝血之作[Rose][Rose][Rose] “爱”这个主题在当今之世特别需要[ThumbsUp]</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">葛芳雯</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">热烈祝贺演出圆满成功！你的独白非常有感染力！音乐配得十分和谐！演员表演很到位！高质量[ThumbsUp][ThumbsUp][ThumbsUp][Rose][Rose][Rose]辛苦获得圆满的回报！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">徐挺的老公</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">非常好！ 有些演员可以说很专业了 他觉得是咱们渥村人一起联欢的好契机。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">徐挺</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">亲爱的 你真是辛苦啦！我觉得这部作品 也是你自己献给人生的礼物 所以很多情感交错复杂的。 我很喜欢。如果非要挑毛病 我只能说 对我的口味来讲有点重，sad</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-18.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.81875" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">Luna</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">您好石静老师，你们不仅仅是在表演，而是在用艺术触动人心，让观众感受美与力量，艺术是一种无声的语言，而你们的作品讲述了最动人的故事，感谢你们带来的感动！继续坚持你们的梦想，你们的才华和努力值得更大的舞台[Hug][Hug][Hug]</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">李坤</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">热烈祝贺石静姐的整台戏剧演出圆满成功！虽然也有不尽人意的地方，但是舞台上的每个细节都扣人心弦，你用专业人士的视角和努力为大家带来了精彩的作品，在这小小的舞台上绽放得淋漓尽致！真的期待未来还能看到更多精彩作品，继续在艺术星河中闪耀✨。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">也心疼你，在这过去一年里，为了这场演出你花费了那么多心血，接下来你应该好好休息休息了。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">多伦多话剧团 - 边红丽</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">今天演出很成功！你的学生很努力也很用心，＂简爱＂的一组演员很棒，你所有付出和辛苦教学都是值得的！ 你瘦了好多，别太拼了多保重身体。好好腄一觉明天的演出会更精彩！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">金晓蕾</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">渥村的艺友们一定都很庆幸在渥太华有石老师的存在！！！石老师在渥村培养了一大群表演艺术爱好者，创作出了许多高水平的，难忘的艺术作品，向石老师致敬！！！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">林平</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">非常震撼[ThumbsUp][Rose]仅一年时间，把普通人打造成能登台表演的演员，也是一种奇迹了！</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-19.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.4265625" data-w="1280" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">幕后工作人员群 - 崔毅</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">25-03-28 - 一年多的时光悄然流转，由【静美艺术空间】出品，石静老师执导的《心声》，像一场悉心培育的花事，终于在渥太华的舞台上尽情绽放！这支由本土演职团队组成的“多国部队”，从零起步，硬是将中外经典熬成了一锅香气四溢的“双语火锅”——东西合璧，滋味浓烈，中外观众都沉浸在这股热腾腾的文化氛围中，仿佛被沁人心脾的香气熏陶得有些微醺。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">从最初的策划，到四季流转中的高强度“修炼”，导演示范到嗓子冒烟，演员们排练到脚步发软，汗水浇灌着每一处细节，将经典打磨成了一件栩栩如生的艺术珍品。说这是在排戏，倒不如说是在锤炼一支能文能武、雅俗共赏的“文化精锐之师”！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">展演接近尾声，我们共唱《我和你》，演员们与观众近距离握手相拥，那耳目一新的经典“变形记”终于幻化成熟。脑海中的生鲜画面久久难以淡出。演员们的每个眼神、每句台词，都在自信地宣告：瞧，这才是经典该有的模样！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">站在台上的演员们和剧组的幕后团队，谢幕时脸上洋溢着真挚与从容，那一刻，或许是为角色的灵魂而感怀，或许是为自己一路走来的坚守而欣慰。 无论如何，这场“双语火锅”早已化作艺术的暖流，用炽热与真情，为渥太华的舞台烙下了难以磨灭的独特印记。而摄影摄像团队为能够记录下从导演到所有剧组演职人员每一刻的感人瞬间，而深感荣幸与自豪。我们影像团队的摄影以定格的瞬间凝固永恒之美，摄像则以流动的视角编织完整的艺术叙事。多机位协同运作，辅以精准的光影调度与声音渲染，将舞台艺术的每一个维度都完整留存。这些珍贵的影像，是对艺术过程的忠实记录，而在完成后期剪辑之后的作品，将会是对创作灵魂的二次诠释，敬请期待。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">【静美艺术空间】出品，必属精品。</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-20.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.2650508209538702" data-w="1279" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">演员群 - 王雯</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">谢谢您又请大家伙儿吃了一顿饭，还有在一起尽情欢乐！您的事业心让人敬佩，您的为人同样让人感动！第一次参加您策划组织的活动，自始至终都感到很轻松愉快，因为您和您的管理团队处处为演员着想，事无巨细地周到安排，大家没有后顾之忧，全力以赴投入到节目的排练中；您的强大的凝聚力又造就了一支强有力的后勤保障队伍，在演出过程中方方面面的服务，打消了演员的紧张心理，大家能够正常发挥顺利演出。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">总之，有幸加入到这个团队，和大家一起努力完成了一件大事，是终生难忘的经历，衷心感谢您！您辛苦了，现在可以好好休息一下，回归家庭，帮先生洗洗碗，做回一个温柔的妻子，</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">一只依人的小鸟!</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">[Salute][Salute][Salute][Worship][Worship][Worship][Rose][Rose][Rose]</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-21.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="1.3260359655981235" data-w="1279" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">王峰</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">谢谢石老师过去几个月的指导和帮助，为您认真，专业，和敬业的精神所感动，非常感谢！！看您帮大家排练那么累一直都感到很心疼和感动，终于见识到了什么是真正的专业和敬业了！！！[ThumbsUp][ThumbsUp][ThumbsUp][Rose][Rose][Rose]</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">赵焕茹 - 我的感想：</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">刚了解到心声演出的时候，我从来没有想到我会加入“听妈妈讲故事”这个节目，毕竟听起来就是专属于小朋友和父母辈的。没想到机会就这样来到了我面前，被节目新颖有深度的构思打动的我没有理由拒绝，由此开启了一段难忘的旅程。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">在长达几个月的排练过程中，我们遇到过很多困难，有时进度受阻，有时人员变动，排练地点对于不开车的我还很难抵达，不过最终我们的节目一点点成型。在这个过程中我收获了十足的成就感，并与剧组成员们建立了友谊。最后进剧场彩排和演出更是前所未有的经历，让我有幸见识到舞台背后的组织调度过程，也体验了一次站在聚光灯下的明星的感受。</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">非常感谢石静老师以及其他所有剧组成员，我们为同一个目标共同努力的经历我将永远珍藏心中，期待下一次合作！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">陈学义</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">这些日子您太辛苦了，要好好休息几天。通过这次活动，向您学到了很多宝贵的东西，特别是您严谨的工作作风，给我留下深刻的印象。希望有机会再向您请教和合作！祝好！</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;">Nichol 李</span></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;">隔空与石静老师握手?您和全体演职人员倾注心血的“心声”双语话剧，带给我们的是一场直抵心灵的艺术盛宴。你们的创新，专业、认真，和细致让人动容，你们用行动诠释了对舞台的热爱和对自己的成全！</span></span></p><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-22.jpg" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.6890625" data-w="1280" style="width:578px;height:398px;" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><section><span leaf="" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;">CHINRADIO 97.9FM 渥太华中文电台</span></span><b data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span textstyle="" style="font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;">，由CHIN RADIO和渥太华华人社区服务中心联合主办，岁月如歌文艺沙龙协办，感谢您的关注和分享，欢迎留言点评。</span></span></b></section><section style="text-align: center;"><img src="spotlight-shi-jing-stage-part2/shi-jing-stage-part2-23.png" class="lf-article-img" data-ratio="0.7084639498432602" data-w="319" type="block" data-aistatus="1"  /></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p>
